<title>Why does the document keep reloading?</title>

<p>
 If<app>Atril</app> detects that the document you have open has changed (perhaps because another program has modified it), it will automatically reload the document and display the most recent version for you.
</p>

<p>
 If the document is deleted while you are still viewing it, it will still remain open.
</p>

